          <div class="pros-cons">
            <div class="pros">
              <h4>What We Like</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Dual card slots for professional peace of mind</li>
                <li>Full-size HDMI port</li>
                <li>Excellent ergonomics and deep grip</li>
                <li>Huge lens selection</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="cons">
              <h4>Trade-offs</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>4K60 has a 1.5x crop</li>
                <li>Rolling shutter in full-frame video</li>
                <li>Screen resolution is merely average</li>
                <li>Burst rate drops with highest quality RAWs</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
